Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個人一定\N都要成為Meister-乙HiME喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（畢業照片\N～埃爾斯汀·賀最後的微笑～)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我明明就是腳受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果連這種事都讓妳幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，接下來幫妳洗身體喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒學姊教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒學姊教了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，妮娜也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.99,0:01:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始服務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛…愛莉卡…不…不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要，不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑嫩嫩～軟綿綿～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，好慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張是妳的份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前出去的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡硬拖著我們去拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明就說不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會很寶貝它的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們現在在這裡的證據啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記的…永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我得寫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我無可取代的摯友們
